What We Offer

Our Services

Preventive Health services

  • Preventive Medical Check-ups
  • Health Risk Assessments (HRA)
  • Biometric Screening
  • Health Talks
  • Stress Management
  • Comprehensive Medical Assessment for new employees to assess their health status and fitness for long term employment (Pre-employment and post-employment check-ups).

Clinical Services

  • Outpatient Clinic 
  • Radio and Laboratory Diagnostics
  • Cardiology
  • Mental Health Clinic
  • Endocrinology
  • Pain Clinic
  • Gastroenterology
  • Gynecology 
  • Pediatrics

Occupational Health Services

  • American Heart Association First Aid, CPR, BLS and ACLS training courses
  • Medical manpower sourcing and management for organizations
  • Pre-employment medical screening 
  • Onsite clinical service provision to organizations
  • Annual or bi-annual medical screening exercises for organizations
  • Medical and Emergency Health Training of medical and non-medical personnel
